[10:57:30    56] +  traversal now lives in the exported `cJSON_GetArrayItem_ffi` boundary, and
[10:57:30    56] +  the other exported array-index operations call that entry point.
[10:57:30    56] +- Converted implementation helper `skip_utf8_bom` to safe Rust. Exported parse
[10:57:30    56] +  entry points now create input byte slices at the FFI boundary and pass them to
