[10:59:16     7] - Removed the implementation-only `get_array_item` helper. The raw linked-list
[10:59:16     7]   traversal now lives in the exported `cJSON_GetArrayItem_ffi` boundary, and
[10:59:16     7]   the other exported array-index operations call that entry point.
[10:59:16     7] - Converted implementation helper `skip_utf8_bom` to safe Rust. Exported parse
[10:59:16     7]   entry points now create input byte slices at the FFI boundary and pass them to
[10:59:16     7]   the non-exported parse implementation, which uses the slice for BOM detection
[10:59:16     7]   while preserving the existing `parse_buffer` fields for the rest of the
[10:59:16     7]   parser.
[10:59:16     7] - Split `utf16_literal_to_utf8`: added a safe slice/index
[10:59:16     7]   `utf16_literal_to_utf8_bytes` decoder that performs the UTF-16 escape
[10:59:16     7]   validation and UTF-8 byte writes. The existing raw-pointer helper remains as
